'''Centrally Controlled Independent Replicant''' or '''CCIR''', was a type of remote-control technology used by [[Loronar Corporation/Legends|Loronar Corporation]] in [[synthdroid]]s and [[Needle fighter]]s.

CCIR technology allowed multiple automatons to be controlled by large central [[Computer/Legends|computers]] rather than a large number of miniaturized [[Droid/Legends|droid]] brains. The technology relied on near-instantaneous transmission between programmable crystals. The need for only minimal internal computers cut the construction cost for such droids although the cost of programmable crystals proved high until Loronar began enslaving [[Tsil]]s from [[Nam Chorios/Legends|Nam Chorios]] in order to accomplish the instant communication needed.

